description:
Data extracted from the PanCancer Atlas initiative on the GDC in Aug 2016. Clinical information about patient cases in the TCGA project. 

Note: Participants were filtered using the PanCancer Atlas whitelist (table Whitelist_ParticipantBarcodes )  

More details: BigQuery table: isb-cgc:pancancer_atlas.clinical_PANCAN_patient_with_followup 
and https://gdc.cancer.gov/about-data/publications/pancanatlas
friendlyName: PanCancer Filtered Clinical With Patient Follow-up
